\v 2 Amakhosi omhlaba azimisela\x + Hlu. 5.3.\x*, lababusi benza ugobe ndawonye\x + Hlu. 5.3.\x* bemelene leN\nd kosi\nd* njalo bemelene logcotshiweyo wayo\x + Hlab. 45.7. Joha. 1.41.\x*, \add besithi\x + Eks. 18.4.\x*\add*:
\v 3 Asiqamule izibopho zabo, silahle intambo zabo zisuke kithi\x + Jer. 5.5.\x*.
\v 4 Ohlezi emazulwini\x + Isa. 40.22.\x* uzahleka\x + Hlab. 37.13. 59.8. Zaga 1.26.\x*, iNkosi izabahleka usulu\x + Jobe 22.19.\x*\x + Hlab. 37.13. 59.8. Zaga 1.26.\x*.
\v 5 Khona izakhuluma kubo entukuthelweni yayo, ibethuse ngokuvutha kolaka lwayo.
\v 6 Kube kanti mina ngibekile iNkosi yami phezu kweZiyoni, intaba yami engcwele.
