\v 7 Ngizalandisa ngesimiso: IN\nd kosi\nd* ithe kimi: Wena uyiNdodana yami, lamuhla ngikuzele\x + Seb. 13.33. Heb. 1.5. 5.5. Mat. 14.33. Mat. 3.17.\x*.
\v 8 Cela kimi, ngizanika izizwe \add zibe\add* yilifa lakho, lemikhawulo yomhlaba \add ibe\add* yimfuyo yakho\x + Hlab. 22.27. 72.8. Hlab. 89.27. Dan. 7.14.\x*.
\v 9 Uzazephula\x + Jobe 34.24. Hlab. 89.23.\x* ngentonga yensimbi\x + Isam. 2.27. 12.5. 19.15.\x*, uziphahlaze njengembiza yebumba\x + Isa. 30.14. Jer. 19.11.\x*.
\v 10 Ngakho-ke hlakaniphani makhosi, lilayeke bahluleli bomhlaba.
